        " عَلِيٌّ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"مَنْ أَخَذَ عَلَى تَعْلِيمِ اَلْقُرْآنِ أَجْراً كَانَ حَظَّهُ يَوْمَ اَلْقِيَامَةِ \"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3675 - Imam Ali ibn Abi Talib (as) said:\n\"Whoever takes payment for teaching the Quran, his share will be [taken] on the Day of Judgment.\""
        ]
